snippet.title: TERE DIL MEIN - Rito Riba | Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair | Rajat Nagpal | Rana Sotal | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Tere Dil Mein featuring Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair.

Audio Credits :-
Singer : Rito Riba
Music Composer : Rajat nagpal
Lyrics : Rana sotal
Music composed , produced and programmed by : Rajat Nagpal 
Mixed and Mastered by : Shadab Rayeen 
Guitars : Rhythm Shaw 
Dholak & Tabla Raju : Sardar and Team 
Chorus : Sonu 
Harmonium : Paras Chopra 
Keys : Rajat Nagpal
Recorded by Rahul Sharma @ Studio 504

Production house : RS Films and Production
Director : Anishh 2.O
EP : Rahul Sahel 
Director Ad : Rajat Yadav & Aashish
Dop : Vikcee
Dop Ac : Rahul Sabharwal
Ac : Rashwinder

Elvish and jannat makeup : Prabh makeover
Art : Karma art

https://www.virginmusic.com/

Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das, Nishtha Sikroria

Optima Insurance Brokers Private Limited (https://optima.co.in/)

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

#teredilmein #elvishyadav #elvish #jannat #jannatzubair #ritoriba

snippet.title: Bebe Main Badmash Banuga (Trailer) Jagjeet Sandhu - Aveera - Releasing 06-Feb-26
snippet.description:
Friday Russh Motion Pictures proudly presents the upcoming Punjabi film "Bebe Main Badmash Banuga"
Starring the immensely talented Jagjeet Sandhu and introducing a promising new face Aveera Singh Masoon. Today, we officially launch the Trailer of the film, giving you a glimpse into a gripping journey

Releasing Worldwide in Cinemas 6th February 2026, Watch the Trailer, share your thoughts in the comments, and stay connected for more updates.

Movie Credits
Movie Name: Bebe Main Badmash Banuga
Releasing Date: 06 February 2026
Starring: Jagjeet Sandhu, Aveera Singh Masson, Ashish Duggal, Sanju Solanki, Paramveer Singh, Satwant Kaur, Rahul Jungral, Ikatar Singh, Jass Longowalia, Guri Toor, Beant Singh, Brijesh Sharma
Story & Directed By: Sukhminder Dhanjal
Produced By: Rrupaali Gupta, Jagjeet Sandhu
Screenplay: Nihal Purba & Gurpreet Bhullar
Dialogues: Gurpreet Bhullar

Leaf Records Presents

Song - Bachke

SONG LYRICS:

Sohni Rann wangu Lishkaake kaddiya
Jhotey bande saare jhotiya ne gaddiya
Dollara de thabbe ni
leerheya te lggey ni
Akh ne lakka di takseem maarli
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Minti ni koi Be-hisaab pee gye 
2.5-3 kille da kmaad pee gye
baithe‚Äôan hayatt lehra-behra‚Äôn lgiyaa‚Äôn
gaddi jinne mull di shraab pee gye
Kaagza bagair koley peaa asla nange hathyaar pye ne cheer faarh lyi
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Swa ser de gya dealer choti da sirrey lggi pyi aa gal maal aali v 
Thandi kitti hoyi aa rlaake bhasma‚Äôn garam taseero aa Imphal aali v 
Khaan te Smaan Khulla dulla chlda akh hoyi pyi aa red bean naal di
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Saade bina gal bndi ni gerhi routa te eve ta mandeera gerhe 20 laundiyaa
Murhde flata nu lai jaayiyee raunka baad vich pariyaa ni jee laundiya
kalli- kalli hath‚Äôn vich kri firde jehri-jehri nigaa ch haseen chaarhli
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

snippet.title: Gal Sun: Je Tu Labda Wafa Firda (4K Video) Rackstar Ft. Sabaat Batin | New Song
snippet.description:
Song: Gal Sun (Je Tu Labda Wafa Firda)
Singer: Sabaat Batin
Lyrics/Composition: Sabaat Batin
Rapper: Rackstar
Music Prod. Rackstar
Mix/Master: Rackstar
Director: Rafaqat Ali
Label: SkillMill Records

lyrics:
Je Tu Labda Wafa Firda Nahi Labni
Roop Dooja Ae Saza Da Sajan Sajni
Jadon Apna Begana Hoya Takdeya Nahi
Rondeyaan Nu Thaan Nahi Tenu Ae Labni
Asi Aa Deewane Bas
Te Sade Kol Khazane Nai
Te Jinna Kol Khazane Nai
Laundi Ohna Naal Yaraane Nai
Duniya Matlabi Duniya
Sun Ke Na Kar Ansuniyaan
Sun O Gal Sun Dilbar Jaani
Jag Wafa Teri Nadaani
Na Koi Tere Gham Da Haani
Rajak ve Jhuthe Jhuthi Rani
Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani
Raja Jhuthe Jhuthi Rani
Oh Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani
Main Fadhan Ohde Dhokhe Aggon Pandi Aa Kahani
Oh Kehndi Kar Vishvaas Haigi Nahiyo Wish Khaas
Dena Chaundi Dhokha Nahi Si Ho Gayi Naadaani
Naadaan Nahi Ae Hoshiyar Bahot
Duniya Ae Kise Di Nahi Ede Yaar Bahut
Tu Maan Baitha Ehnu Aakhri
Janda Nahi Veere Haige Ehde Yaar Bahut
Na Kari Yaara Pyar Nahin Milni Wafa
Ohna Pyar Haiga Sarna Ni Apni Dafa
Haan Kari Izhaar Na Tu Kari Aitbaar
Tu Kinu Sooli Chadhna Main Likh ke Dawan
Chann Chann Aakhein Jihnu Raataan Ohne Pauniyan Ne
Pani Jihne Rang Chadhaya Aggaan Ohne Launiyan Ne
Kal Kujh Nai Je Sochna Te Soch Ajj Hi
Ajj Baras Pai Kal Hona Gajj Hi
Kar Faisla Je Ajj Kal Fer Hona Kakh Ni
Baki Daseya Main Agge Yaara Teri Marzi
Sun O Gal Sun Dilbar Jaani
Jag Wafa Teri Naadaani
Na Koi Tere Gham Da Haani
Raja Jhoothe Jhoothi Rani
Koi Nahi Daur Reh Gaye Ve
Pyara Te Khumaraan De
O Bikde Ne Dil Jaani Lakha Te Hazara Che Vey
Koi Nai Daur Reh Gaye Ve
Pyara Te Khumaraan De
